‘Trust Your Product’ is an innovating and inspiring project started in Geneva, Switzerland that is aimed at the development of a mobile platform that will allow to reliably detect counterfeited products whether it concerns luxury goods, medicine, or baby meal.
The solution offered by this project will let anyone verify the originality of a great variety of products using technologically sophisticated mechanism integrated into a user-friendly dedicated smartphone application. The creators of this inspiring project are now seeking generous community support on the crowdfunding platform of Indiegogo and they are welcoming everyone to support the project. The potential, advantages, and possibilities raised by this project are immense and it will greatly help in the eradication of fake products floating in the market.
The Indiegogo Campaign is located on the web at:
www.indiegogo.com/projects/trust-your-product-feel-safe-mobile-security and supporters from all around the world can back this Swiss originated project from $25 to $30000. Each pledge will have a reward of its own and the latter one will be rewarded by the partnership with the company.
About Trust Your Product
‘Trust Your Product’ is a novel technologically advanced mobile platform that is being developed in Switzerland and will help to certify originality of a large gamma of products along the entire supply chain including final customers. The creators are now seeking community support for this great project on Indiegogo and they are welcoming everyone from around the world to generously support this initiative.
